well today is kinda depressing. its the last day of spring break and tomarrow we go back to the endless hell-hole they call school.my doggy cant walk anymore :( poor thing will be dead soon. and i realized a lot today.im beyond bored with my life and im so sick of daily routines. i think thats part of my problem.same things everyday and nuthing to look forward too . not even anything worth waking up for (for that matter)and i know disembarking on myself doesnt help. but it feels good to vent sometimes.and on top of that i got the most appalling,repugnant hair cut ever.


for a few seconds, it didn't really seem necessary to breathe...

yesterday morning me and christine went tanning and went to summerset.then last night i went and saw miss congeniality 2 with the CGs :) then me steph and alaina went to cold stone and had sum great ice cream. alaina has an interveiw there today.then we went back to my house for a little and then we went on a road trip to take stephy home and alaina spend the night and we prolly will hit up the tanning beds this morning

well thursday was the last day of school for 10 days. thank god!i had softball till like 7:30 and christine came over atfer work. we stole my moms car and went up to blockbuster and got the weridest gayest movie ive ever seen.then friday we woke up and went tanning.im goin to try to go tanning like everyday this break.then after a disapointment and a few tears i went over to kristins and kristins brother was home from college this weekend (my best friend joe lorr) so he took us to get froggies at 1 in the morning lol there so cute and little. mines cheech and kris's is chong :)

new journal - thanks kris 

might think i'm losing my mind but i will shy away from the specifics 'cuz i don't want you to know where i am 'cuz then you'll see my heart in the saddest state it's ever been. this is no place to try & live my life. stop right there.. that's exactly where i lost it see that line.. well i never should have crossed it. stop right there.. well i never should have said that it's the very moment that i wish that i could take back. i'm sorry for the person i became, i'm sorry that it took so long for me to change. i'm ready to try to never become that way again 'cuz who i am hates who i've been. who i am hates who i've been. i talked to absolutely no one, couldn't keep to myself enough & the things i bottled inside i finally begun to create so much pressure that i'd soon blow up. i heard the reverberating footsteps syncing up to the beating of my heart & i was positive that unless i got myself together i would watch me fall apart.
